00:00:36.650 --> 00:00:39.870
So that the Laplace
transform is just

00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:51.950
s squared y, sy, and that's
the transform of our equation.

00:00:51.950 --> 00:00:53.250
No problem.

00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:57.270
