00:01:31.410 --> 00:01:33.190
It's a product.

00:01:33.190 --> 00:01:36.670
The transform of the
solution that we want

00:01:36.670 --> 00:01:41.330
is that transform
times that transform.

00:01:41.330 --> 00:01:46.510
This is the transform
of the impulse response.

00:01:46.510 --> 00:01:50.470
This is the transform
of the right-hand side.

00:01:50.470 --> 00:01:54.890
Now I just have a Laplace
transform question.

00:01:54.890 --> 00:01:59.840
Suppose my transform
